ComicInfo.Title: What Your Big Sister Done (a.k.a Dark Streets, Snap City) The Conclusion!
ComicInfo.Summary: It Girl has seen the true face of her enemy, and she's confronting LaLa Wah-Wah on the villain's own turf: inside the video game dimension! It's a dangerous showdown, but with the Atomics rallying behind her, It Girl can't lose. Concluding the first arc of Image's newest hit series.
